+Additionally, all the data received in the xApp is also written to `DB_DIR/DB_NAME` or `/tmp/xapp_db_<random-numbers>` (if `DB_DIR=/tmp/`) in case that offline data processing is wanted (e.g., Machine Learning/Artificial Intelligence applications). You can browse the data using e.g., sqlitebrowser. To disable this database feature, compile FlexRIC with `-DXAPP_DB=NONE_XAPP`.
 
